name: painting with a camera - Piece 07
description:
This painting is the result of an experiment using a camera, sunlight, movements and a tree (Caryocar brasiliense, also known as "pequizeiro").

The photograph is not photoshopped. The effects were achieved through long-exposure and other specific camera settings.

This is part of an 8-piece collection. Pieces 1-4 are collored and 5-8 are black & white.
